(2, 472, 'Trish Gray', 'trish@oreillyschool.com', '', '209.118.197.2', '2011-04-24 01:44:59', '2011-04-24 08:44:59', 'WOW, what a show!  This was my first time seeing Foreverland, and I must say that although I was expecting a great time, I did not expect such an incredible level of talent and showmanship.  I danced so hard, I ended up on stage during "The Girl is Mine".  Ha!  It is obvious that you all have a great amount of love and care for the music of MJ, and performing Off the Wall and Thriller in their entireties was an enormous treat for this huge fan.  Thank you SO MUCH!  I will definitely be seeing you all again!  xoxo', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_8; en-us) AppleWebKit/533.19.4 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.0.3 Safari/533.19.4', '', 0, 0),
(3, 228, 'Trish Gray', 'trish@oreillyschool.com', '', '209.204.147.53', '2011-04-25 11:33:08', '2011-04-25 18:33:08', '6/24 is my birthday and there''s no WAY I''m missing this show!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_8; en-us) AppleWebKit/533.19.4 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.0.3 Safari/533.19.4', '', 0, 0),
(4, 472, 'geri brose', 'geribrose@gmail.com', '', '174.58.51.228', '2011-04-26 20:41:15', '2011-04-27 03:41:15', 'Seeing the band for the first time live was a total thrill for Alex''s Dad and me....My goodness...you boys rock!  Can''t wait to see the next show...hoping for the East Coast this coming Summer.  Love to all of you amazing performers,.and special hugs to Alex Brose.........Michael LIVES on because of you guys.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.1; en-US; rv:1.9.2.16) Gecko/20110319 Firefox/3.6.16 ( .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET4.0C)', '', 0, 0),
(6, 772, 'Trish Gray', 'trish@oreillyschool.com', '', '70.36.129.143', '2011-05-14 01:19:29', '2011-05-14 08:19:29', 'Guys - I am your new biggest fan.  Thank you SO MUCH for a great show tonight!\r\n\r\nI will see you next at Mezzanine in SF.  The 24th of June happens to be my birthday!  So I have a request for you to either:\r\n    1) Play something from the Invincible album; \r\nOR\r\n    2) Play the full-length video version of Thriller.  I would be MORE than happy to get up on stage and lead the audience in the full Thriller dance.  :-)\r\n\r\nThanks again, you''re the BEST.\r\nTrish', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_8; en-us) AppleWebKit/533.19.4 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.0.3 Safari/533.19.4', '', 0, 0),
(7, 627, 'Ron Yarolimek', 'ronyarolimek@yahoo.com', '', '76.206.48.136', '2011-05-16 19:05:23', '2011-05-17 02:05:23', 'Pittsburg Pops Series........would like location &amp; time.  Can''t find it anywhere and we''d like our Foreverland fix!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1; rv:2.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0.1', '', 0, 0),
(8, 627, 'Adam', 'adam@foreverlandsf.com', '', '66.117.143.148', '2011-05-17 09:16:39', '2011-05-17 16:16:39', 'Hi Ron!\r\nPittsburg Pops happens from 6-8pm at the Plaza at 5th and Railroad Avenue in Pittsburg, CA. <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Railroad+Ave+%26+E+5th+St+Pittsburg,+CA&amp;aq=&amp;sll=38.031985,-121.883682&amp;sspn=0.010986,0.014699&amp;gl=us&amp;g=Railroad+Ave+%26+E+5th+St,+Pittsburg,+CA+94565&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=Railroad+Ave+%26+E+5th+St,+Pittsburg,+Contra+Costa,+California+94565&amp;ll=38.030853,-121.884212&amp;spn=0.010986,0.014699&amp;z=16" rel="nofollow">Here''s a map</a>. \r\n\r\nYou can find some more information here: <a href="http://www.shopoldtown.com/PittsburgPops.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.shopoldtown.com/PittsburgPops.htm</a>\r\n\r\nI added some additional details to the listing above. Hope to see you there!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_8) AppleWebKit/534.24 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/11.0.696.68 Safari/534.24', '', 7, 3),
(9, 462, 'Danielle M.', 'danielle.modesto@me.com', '', '66.65.47.76', '2011-05-28 10:06:07', '2011-05-28 17:06:07', 'Show was amazing!!  I am a die-hard MJ fan but never had the opportunity to see him perform live.  I felt like this was the closest I could get to it.  You guys are wonderful performers and musicians.  I could not stop dancing or smiling the entire evening!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_8; en-us) AppleWebKit/533.19.4 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.0.3 Safari/533.19.4', '', 0, 0),
(10, 462, 'Andrea Armendariz', 'a98andrea@hotmail.com', '', '74.72.42.164', '2011-05-29 06:37:29', '2011-05-29 13:37:29', 'I was at the Brooklyn Bowl Tribute concert for MJ . It was fabulous!!!! You guys really nailed it with the singing and all the instruments really gave it that full rich sound that Michael loved. I am so glad I went.The crowd was really into your performance. You are right up there with the best MJ performances I have seen since he passed. Great,great job!!!!!!!! Please come to NYC again ANYTIME!!!!', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.0; WOW64; Trident/4.0; FunWebProducts; GTB6.6; SLCC1; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; Media Center PC 5.0; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; .NET4.0C; AskTbLMW2/5.11.3.15590; BRI/2; BO1IE8_v1;ENUS)', '', 0, 0),
