(12, 770, 'Ed', 'Dontparkthere25@yahoo.com', '', '76.218.216.51', '2011-06-02 16:13:33', '2011-06-02 23:13:33', 'For the saturday show at Dan''s , are there advance Tix or Tix at the door? How much is the cover?', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; U; CPU iPhone OS 4_3 like Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/533.17.9 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.0.2 Mobile/8F190 Safari/6533.18.5', '', 0, 0),
