(18, 215, 'shaw', 'shaw3222@aol.com', '', '76.102.197.81', '2011-06-28 12:27:01', '2011-06-28 19:27:01', '"Vegas baby, Vegas" ~\r\n\r\nand NYC, too!\r\ncongratulations\r\noutstanding -every aspect\r\nsuprised though, rushed credits\r\nfor the names of each group member with \r\na spotlight on each face-  crowd would roll with that-\r\nyou deserve to be known by name as well as group-\r\namazing back-up \r\n charismatic , sexy  vocalists  --  but withoutsuperb musiciansthere would be no performance!! I especially adored the rapper- hip- hop and the adorable moment of spot on stunning  Janet Jackson... a real compliment to her with great moves - first rate addition\r\nlove to assist in promo/press/marketing/ attendance/ infectious enthusiam-- here i am -- use me  please ... best .shaw', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 5.1; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.0.4506.2152; .NET CLR 3.5.30729)', '', 0, 0),
